org.netbeans.modules.java.api.common.ant

Interface PackageModifierImplementation


  • public interface PackageModifierImplementation
    Provide API for manipulating with project packages. This API is associated with org.netbeans.api.java.queries.AccessibilityQuery. Packages passed to exportPackageAction method were marked by AccessibilityQuery to be either public or private.

    1.49
